nodeDataArray.text:
In this model we are taking relevant data from the stg_shopify_orders  and the stg_shopify_order_item models.

The output table mrt_orders takes all revenue KPIs are from the  stg_shopify_order_item model and aggregates them at order level. The data selected from the stg_shopify_orders are all other order level data

The output table mrt_order_items takes all all relevant order level info from the stg_shopify_orders model and joins them with the stg_shopify_order_items.
Aggregate revenue KPIs from line items table at order level
The refund date is defined as the date of the first refund for that order (this applies in case items from the same order were refunded in different dates)
Join line items data with order level data
Join order level data with aggregated line items data
